## President's Report

<pre>
Stephen Frost, Héctor Orón Martínez, and I met the past few days in
Indianapolis. We got signatories updated on all of our bank accounts
and met with our wealth management adviser at Merrill Lynch and are
planning some account consolidations. We also worked heavily in RT and
got both the board and treasurer queues to a more reasonable
level. Héctor should have full access to handle all treasury tasks now
but I continue to be available to assist with treasury tasks as
needed.

Continued thanks to SPI Vice President, Stephen Frost, for handling
contracting with SPI's contractors. Stephen continues to do a
fantastic job working with our contractors and legal counsel.
</pre>

