## Any other business

Stephen Frost reminded directors to be more responsive in addressing
mails sent to the board address as this is the primary contact point
for SPI board members and directors.

Nominations for SPI's 2022 board election open 2022-07-01. Four board
seats are up for election this year. If you are interested in running
for the SPI board, feel free to reach out to current board members to
get information about the SPI board and its director needs.

It was decided that SPI would not renew the expiring Drizzle trademark
due to the project being abandoned many years ago.

SPI is very interested in having folks help us move things forward,
and you don't have to be a board member to help!  We have started
working on a specific document of things that we need help with and
ideas we have about what can be done, including- project liaison (from
SPI back to projects to ask them about how SPI can help them and other
things). We are working on moving the member website towards a
django/python stack for this which will hopefully be easier for new
folks to help with), and there's more that volunteers could definitely
help us out with!  Of course, we also need folks on the board who can
commit to making the regular meetings and handling tasks which need to
be done.

